data.title: Vincent Fang (entrepreneur)
data.meta_description: Vincent Fang Kang, GBS, JP is a entrepreneur in the garment industry. He is the former chairman and leader of the Liberal Party of Hong Kong and former member of the Legislative Council of Hong Kong, representing the Wholesale and Retail functional constituency.
